Ex-BBnaija housemate Lucy Edet has shared an intimate part of herself with fans and followers on social media. The TV personality had a question and answer session with fans who wanted to know more about her personal life, which she shared via her insta stories. The reality star was more than willing to answer the many questions of her fans and in the process shared shocking details about herself. One fan asked if the reality TV star enjoys secret affairs or just doesn’t have a man in her life and Lucy said; “I enjoy my privacy! But I’m also single till I’m married. Another extremely inquisitive fan decided to delve deeper by asking Lucy if she is still a virgin to which the 31-year-old responded: “Yes o! Till thy kingdom come.”